    <item>
      <title>由于成本上升、收入意外下降，德国商业银行股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/handelsbanken-earnings-miss-as-growing-costs-draw-more-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典商业银行 (Svenska Handelsbanken AB) 的费用上升和净利息收入下降，使新任首席执行官迈克尔·格林 (Michael Green) 对成本控制的关注受到质疑，导致该银行股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/handelsbanken-earnings-miss-as-growing-costs-draw-more-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 04:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行加强了对长期政府债券上涨的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/pboc-steps-up-rhetoric-against-long-end-government-bond-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行加大了对长期政府债券涨势的口头压制力度，警告可能出现逆转，并暗示市场价格与经济前景之间的不匹配将得到纠正，导致债券走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/pboc-steps-up-rhetoric-against-long-end-government-bond-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国希望Fortescue观点下铁矿石价格升至七周高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/iron-ore-rises-as-fortescue-says-exports-hit-by-mine-disruptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格攀升至七周以来的最高水平，第四大生产商 Fortescue Ltd. 表示，由于西澳大利亚矿山的供应受到干扰，全年出货量可能会处于指导值的下限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/iron-ore-rises-as-fortescue-says-exports-hit-by-mine-disruptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
